Module chav1961.purelib
Package chav1961.purelib.model

Class ContentMetadataFilter

java.lang.Object
chav1961.purelib.model.ContentMetadataFilter
All Implemented Interfaces:
ContentMetadataInterface
public class ContentMetadataFilter
extends java.lang.Object
implements ContentMetadataInterface

This class is a filter for nested ContentMetadataInterface model. It can be used to exclude some part of model from searching/walking.

Since:
0.0.3
Author:
Alexander Chernomyrdin aka chav1961
LastUpdate:
0.0.4

    • ContentMetadataFilter

      public ContentMetadataFilter​(ContentMetadataInterface nested, java.net.URI[] whiteList, java.net.URI[] blackList) throws java.lang.NullPointerException, java.lang.IllegalArgumentException

      Constructor of the class.

      Parameters:
      nested - nested model to make filter for
      whiteList - white list of URI will be retained in the nested model (see ContentMetadataInterface.ContentNodeMetadata.getRelativeUIPath())
      blackList - black list of URI will be excluded from the nested model (see ContentMetadataInterface.ContentNodeMetadata.getRelativeUIPath()). Black list priority is higher than white list
      Throws:
      java.lang.NullPointerException - any arguments are null
      java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - white or black list is null, empty or contains nulls inside

    • ContentMetadataFilter

      public ContentMetadataFilter​(ContentMetadataInterface nested, java.lang.String whiteListRegExp, java.lang.String blackListRegExp) throws java.lang.NullPointerException, java.lang.IllegalArgumentException

      Constructor of the class.

      Parameters:
      nested - nested model to make filter for
      whiteListRegExp - white list URI regular expression will be retained in the nested model (see ContentMetadataInterface.ContentNodeMetadata.getRelativeUIPath())
      blackListRegExp - white list URI regular expression will be excluded from the nested model (see ContentMetadataInterface.ContentNodeMetadata.getRelativeUIPath()). Black list regular expression priority is higher than white list
      Throws:
      java.lang.NullPointerException - any arguments are null
      java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - white or black list is null, empty or has syntax errors
